## Academic Use Notice

This project was developed as an academic assignment for a Multimedia Environment course. 
It demonstrates the implementation of Disney's 12 Principles of Animation in a web-based game.

### Educational Purpose
- Implementation of animation principles in interactive media
- Game development using vanilla JavaScript and HTML5 Canvas
- Object-oriented programming concepts
- Physics simulation and collision detection
- User interface design and user experience

### Attribution
If you use this project for educational or reference purposes, please provide appropriate attribution to the original author and the academic context of the work.
